 * - Handle SSL/non-SSL environments
 *
 * INTEGRATION POINTS:
 * - Hook into 'template_redirect' for output buffering
 * - Integrate with existing cache system
 * - Add CloudFlare API settings (zone ID, API key)
 * - Add BunnyCDN API integration
 * - Add StackPath/MaxCDN integration
 *
 * CDN PROVIDERS TO SUPPORT:
 * - CloudFlare (most popular)
 * - BunnyCDN (affordable)
 * - KeyCDN
 * - StackPath/MaxCDN
 * - Amazon CloudFront
 * - Generic CDN (custom hostname)
 *
 * PERFORMANCE CONSIDERATIONS:
 * - Minimal overhead in URL rewriting
 * - Cache rewritten URLs when possible
 * - Don't rewrite admin URLs
 * - Don't rewrite external URLs
 *
 * @package WPShadow\CoreSupport
 * @since 1.2601.75000
 */

